item.title: Need help makin server go online
item.dc:creator: @javis javis
item.description:
@javis wrote:

OK so heres what you need to do. First go to downloads and find a server that fits yours needs and download it. From there you can start coding it ect. Once you have it exactly how you want it register it on no-ip. Then when your ready open your runserver.bat and get your no-ip running and then you can register it. Until then you cant because you have to have a server running to register it.
Hope that helps if you need more help just pm me
